@Estimator.Api_HostAddress = https://localhost:7121

### 1) Start estimation session from plain description
POST {{Estimator.Api_HostAddress}}/estimate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "Build a .NET application for transceiver EEPROM read/write with offline sync and audit trail."
}

### 2) Continue session with clarification answer (replace session_id)
POST {{Estimator.Api_HostAddress}}/estimate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sessionId": "replace_with_session_id",
  "answer": "Phase 1 must support only SFP/SFP+ and local USB coding box."
}

### 3) Start estimation from document
# Use multipart/form-data with key: file
